{"issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/10807", "repo": "rails", "body": "@josevalim I haven't gotten to the caching part yet \u2013 the idea is to store the classes in a cache, e.g.\r\n\r\n```ruby\r\ndef compile!\r\n  key = get_some_cache_key_for(self)\r\n  @compiled_templates[key] ||= Compiler.compile_template(self)\r\nend\r\n```\r\n\r\nThen the only thing that will happen per-request is the instantiation of a compiled template class and the render call.", "_id": {"$oid": "5237dba6bd3543c1510088a8"}, "issue_id": 10807, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/18742061", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/10807#issuecomment-18742061", "updated_at": "2013-05-31T12:31:33Z", "user": {"subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dasch/subscriptions", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dasch/events{/privacy}", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dasch/repos", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dasch/gists{/gist_id}", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/dasch", "login": "dasch", "gravatar_id": "a9cc05e6a7866e5fa9a7d107b5070174", "html_url": "https://github.com/dasch", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dasch/following{/other_user}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dasch/received_events", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dasch/orgs", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/a9cc05e6a7866e5fa9a7d107b5070174?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Fc6862d63b17d713ee14f3a405d9fde77.png", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dasch/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "id": 6351, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dasch/followers", "type": "User"}, "created_at": "2013-05-31T12:31:33Z", "id": 18742061, "owner": "rails"}
